description:
**__Obtainable Roles:__**
The roles below are obtainable through activity in the server. In order to rank up, you must participate and engage in conversations in any channel with the exception of bot channels. Spamming does not count as a part of your total counted messages.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&933187488053334022>
The bottom of the totem pole. However, this is nothing to be ashamed of as everyone here has been in your shoes. Treat this as your entrance exam into the server and give it all you got!

:small_blue_diamond: <@&933187568944685076>
Congratulations! :confetti_ball: You have engaged in conversations or have participated in the server. You are now recognized as an active member of our community’s family and have earned your place here.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&933187649143980064>
Amazing! You’re near the top of the food chain. You are now acknowledged as one of the most active members of the community due to your time spent here active and your positive impact on the student body. Thank you for being a model student and someone to look up to :partying_face:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------

__**Unique Roles:**__
The roles below are obtainable only through special selection or for miscellaneous reasons.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&933186939614543912> <:GDM:935088198860816394>
Those who have contributed to the AB community through writing, art, or have contributed through other forms.

:small_blue_diamond: <@&933924167575830608>
Our friends in which they may post their Discord link. Check them out in <#933123970943811584>!

:small_blue_diamond: <@&933911363510734869>
Hey, it's your birthday! Have a good time and enjoy your day!

:small_blue_diamond: <@&935594354918187099>
Translators of any official/fanmade AB content. Thank you for your hard work!

--------------------------------------------------------------------------
title: Roles, Part 1
